Oh, sorry, I just realized what you are doing with all these tests.
Since you only really have one test with a nuance on the inputs, the better practice would be to have 1 DataProvider with your different tests as it's inputs.
i.e.
data resolver
{
// typered fields with pdsc files
{ ...}
{...}
// typeref field with pdl files
{ ...}
{ ... }
// inline field with pdsc files
{ ...}
{...}
//inline field with pdl files
{ ...}
{ ...}
}
then your test would be just the one test you had.

